(113, 29, 'artist_content_0_artist_bio', 'With almost 20 years of experience, Megan has made quite a name for herself as one of the top female tattoo artists in the United States. Working diligently on the convention circuit and being featured in numerous magazines worldwide, Megan still awes her fans with her uncanny attention to detail.\r\n\r\nAs a master in both color and black &amp; gray tattooing, she specializes in portrait tattooing and reproduction work – with a twist, making each piece that she works on her own.\r\n\r\nAs of 2012 I can celebrate 21 years exploring tattooing as my primary creative pursuit. I have had the good fortune to enjoy the company of countless interesting individuals and to share in the process of collaborative realization of thier mind’s eye’s desires. The endless diversity of personality and background as well as the universality of our common human experience keeps me inspired and serves to create an air of anticipation for each new experience with a client and the resulting work of art.\r\n\r\nI attempt to allow each piece to say a little about what drives and intigues me as a person. With the most successful tattoos, the piece says a little about me, the wearer and the subject. Just one of many facets of the hard to pin down magic of this art form that has held sway over the human experience for all of recorded history.\r\n\r\nI look forward to many more collaborations on skin, meeting new people, catching up with those already aquainted, personal expressions on canvas, and capturing of my observations on film over the next 21 years and beyond. I am humbly grateful for the support of my loved ones and my many varied clients past, future, and present without which this life long experience would not be possible.'),
